I made this when I was using FindObjectDeformed. I didnt want to keep adding free bitmaps so I thought id make this. I know its nothing big, probably something that wont be used, and I dont even know if it would work, but hey, its the first time making a Fuction.  :P

[scar]
// By Junior
// Will free up to five bitmaps.. I think.
Function FreeBitmapMulti(Bitmap1,Bitmap2,Bitmap3,Bitmap4,Bitmap5:integer): Boolean;
Begin
   If (Bitmap1 > 0) Then
   Begin
     Result:= True
     FreeBitmap(Bitmap1);
    End;
  If (Bitmap2 > 0) Then
   Begin
     Result:= True
     FreeBitmap(Bitmap2);
    End;
  If (Bitmap3 > 0) Then
   Begin
     Result:= True
     FreeBitmap(Bitmap3);
    End;
  If (Bitmap4 > 0) Then
   Begin
     Result:= True
     FreeBitmap(Bitmap4);
    End;
  If (Bitmap5 > 0) Then
   Begin
    Result:= True
    FreeBitmap(Bitmap5);
  End;
End;
[/scar]
